ymptotic constraint on the bandstructure. An analogous trade-off,\nultimately between error rate (reliability) and delay (switching speed) can be\nprojected to persist for all graphitic derivatives. Proceeding thus to a higher\nlevel, a compact model is presented to capture the complex nanoribbon circuits,\nculminating in inverter characteristics, design metrics and layout diagrams.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Apr 2011 17:25:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 May 2011 16:40:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
