igurations to stealthy disordered ground states. These results\nlead to a more complete understanding of the unusual behaviors exhibited by the\nfamily of \"collective-coordinate\" potentials to which the $k$-space overlap\npotential belongs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Apr 2011 13:24:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
